350
00:26:47,899 --> 00:26:50,485
<i>Artemisia vowed that day
to return to Greece...</i>

351
00:26:51,945 --> 00:26:53,655
<i>...only when she could watch it burn.</i>

352
00:26:56,449 --> 00:26:57,492
[GRUNTING]

353
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:08,837
